From a01f602e93c9af01b81cab4a8b1131a699c20960 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tommy Fenton <tfenton445@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 3 May 2026 04:40:50 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] audit: risk gates, logging, heartbeat, reconcile cron, AI
 duration tracking
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- _shared/risk.ts: replace binary OPEN_POSITION with CORRELATED_POSITIONS_CAP
  and BOOK_EXPOSURE portfolio gates (40% equity cap); 5 new tests in risk.test.ts
- signal-engine: structured log() rollout, Taylor/Bobby AbortSignal.timeout +
  duration logging, pingHeartbeat() dead-man ping on HEALTHCHECK_URL, pass
  openPositionCount + bookExposureUsd into RiskContext
- market-intelligence: structured log() rollout, AI call duration logging for
  all Brain Trust experts, system_events write on candle fetch final failure
- post-trade-learn: structured log() rollout, Coach AbortSignal.timeout +
  duration logging
- useSystemState: add lastUpdatedAt timestamp for Realtime-driven UI refresh
- reasons.ts: add CORRELATED_POSITIONS_CAP and BOOK_EXPOSURE gate codes
- position-reconcile/index.ts: new hourly cron — cross-checks Coinbase balances
  against open DB trades; writes journal_entries alerts for orphaned positions
  and ghost DB records
